 Game Notes 
 ~~~~~~~~~~
 FUEL delivers exhilarating, spectacular races, at any time of day in a huge
 range of vehicles. Experience the dynamic weather system and witness how 
 deadly tornadoes and sandstorms affect the way your race plays out. 
 Negotiate diverse terrain from deep snow to arid riverbeds, battle the 
 elements and pull off stunning stunts as you race and explore an epic world
 on an unprecedented scale.
 

 Install Notes
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 1. Extract RARs
 2. Mount or Burn image
 3. Install
 4. Copy Crack to your install folder
 5. Play
